{
  "text": "Does it matter if the pyramid is solid or is made of four thin sides, or is there a difference in effect between those two makes? I am Ra. As an energy collector, the shape itself is the only requirement. From the standpoint of the practical needs of your body complexes, if one is to house one's self in such a shape, it is well that this shape be solid sided in order to avoid being inundated by outer stimuli.",
